@page "/AuditViewerSample"
@using Pixata.Blazor.Auditing.Components
@using Pixata.Blazor.Sample.Data

<h3>Audit Viewer</h3>

<p>This page demonstrates the <code>AuditViewer</code> component, which provides a UI for browsing the audit history of your entities.</p>

<p>The viewer discovers all <code>DbSet&lt;T&gt;</code> properties on your <code>DbContext</code> via reflection, and allows you to select an entity type, search for specific entity IDs, and view a timeline of all changes with property-level diffs.</p>

<AuditViewer TContext="SampleDbContext" />
